&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ritaranchpethospital.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Rita Ranch Pet Hospital&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;an AAHA-accredited practice in Tucson, AZ, is seeking an Associate Veterinarian to join our growing, family-oriented team. This is an excellent opportunity for a veterinarian who values flexibility, collaboration, and a positive workplace culture while practicing high-quality medicine in a well-equipped hospital.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Rita Ranch Pet Hospital, we’ve created more than just a workplace—we’ve built a supportive, close-knit team that feels like family. We genuinely enjoy working together and believe that great medicine starts with great people. Our staff is enthusiastic, engaged, and committed to continuous learning. You’ll be surrounded by teammates who are eager to support one another, share knowledge, and grow together.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We pride ourselves on fostering an environment where ideas are welcomed, teamwork is natural, and everyone’s voice matters. Our approach to medicine is thoughtful and individualized, with a strong focus on patient comfort, client communication, and Fear-Free-inspired handling.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexibility &amp;amp; Work-Life Harmony: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We understand that life outside of work matters. That’s why we offer flexible scheduling options designed to support your personal priorities—whether that means family time, outdoor adventures, or simply maintaining a sustainable pace. We’re committed to helping you create true work-life harmony, where your career complements your life—not competes with it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To further support your success and efficiency, we provide access to modern tools, including AI-driven resources that help streamline workflows, enhance medical documentation, and give you more time to focus on patient care and meaningful client interactions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Compensation: Base salary with production and no negative accrual, plus potential sign-on bonus depending on experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive Benefits: Medical, dental, and vision insurance, HSA contribution, life and disability coverage, 401(k) with match, PTO, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional Development: Generous CE allowance plus paid licensing and membership dues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supportive Team Culture: Work alongside kind, motivated professionals who are invested in each other’s success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Growth Opportunities: Potential to develop into a leadership role if desired&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional Perks: Uniform allowance and a genuinely positive, team-oriented environment &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Life in Tucson, Arizona: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tucson offers beautiful desert scenery, year-round sunshine, and endless outdoor activities. From hiking and biking to a thriving food and arts scene, it’s an ideal place to build both a fulfilling career and a balanced lifestyle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Lakefield Veterinary Group: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of Lakefield Veterinary Group, a family-owned organization, our doctors enjoy the autonomy to practice medicine their way while benefiting from the support and resources of a larger network. We are deeply committed to flexibility, personal well-being, and maintaining a strong, people-first culture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interested?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re looking for a supportive, down-to-earth team where you can grow and feel valued, we’d love to connect. Reach out to Nikki Hanschu at nikki.hanschu@lakefieldvet.com or apply here:&amp;nbsp

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Associate Veterinarian – Join Our Friendly, Supportive Team in the Heart of Minnesota&#39;s Lake Country!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
