&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible Scheduling&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– We are only open on weekdays with family friendly hours of 8-5 so our team can enjoy a better&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;work-life balance&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
