&lt;li&gt;Medical/Dental/Vision Insurance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HSA company contributed account&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lakefield AVMA Membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lakefield AVMA PLIT Policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Voluntary Life and AD&amp;amp;D insurance, long-term care, Accident, Critical Illness, and Hospital Indemnity Employer Paid Life and AD&amp;amp;D&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employer Paid STD and LTD&lt;/li&gt;
