&lt;p&gt;🐾&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;We’re Hiring: Associate Veterinarian&lt;/strong&gt; 🐾&lt;br&gt;📍 &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://canyonpethospital.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Canyon Pet Hospital&lt;/a&gt; | Beaverton, Oregon&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
