&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canyon Pet Hospital has &lt;strong&gt;proudly served the Beaverton community since the 1940s&lt;/strong&gt;, caring for generations of pets and families. Our culture is built on &lt;strong&gt;respect, compassion, and collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;, with a strong emphasis on individualized patient care and excellent client communication. You’ll be supported by experienced veterinarians and a dedicated, compassionate support team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible scheduling&lt;/strong&gt; with standard hours Monday through Friday from 7:30am to 5:30pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive compensation&lt;/strong&gt; including base salary, &lt;strong&gt;monthly production with no negative accrual&lt;/strong&gt;, and a generous sign on bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excellent benefits&lt;/strong&gt; including medical, dental, vision, life insurance, HSA contributions, 401k with match, PTO, CE allowance, license and uniform coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentorship and professional growth&lt;/strong&gt; for both experienced doctors and new graduates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;full-service caseload&lt;/strong&gt; including wellness, diagnostics, surgery, dentistry, pain management, and alternative therapies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Life in Beaverton:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy a vibrant suburban lifestyle with &lt;strong&gt;easy access to Portland’s dining, culture, and amenities&lt;/strong&gt;, along with endless outdoor adventures throughout the Pacific Northwest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Lakefield Veterinary Group:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of a &lt;strong&gt;family-owned organization&lt;/strong&gt;, Canyon Pet Hospital maintains full clinical autonomy while benefiting from the support and resources of Lakefield Veterinary Group.&lt;/p&gt;
