&lt;p&gt;Are you a compassionate, skilled veterinarian looking for an opportunity to make a real difference in your patients, your clients, and your hospital?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&lt;strong&gt; GP or Urgent Care Associate Veterinarian&lt;/strong&gt; to join our dedicated team at &lt;a href=&quot;https://allcare.vet/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-cke-saved-href=&quot;https://allcare.vet/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All Care Animal Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, where we believe every pet and owner deserves the very best in care and comfort.&amp;nbsp;We&#39;re located in beautiful Minneola, Florida, and for the past 30 years, we&#39;ve been proud to serve Lake County&#39;s pet community with love, expertise, and a commitment to excellence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New grads are welcome to apply!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a 4-doctor practice and we have 2 doctors on staff Mon – Fri, along with assigned techs per doctor. Whether it&#39;s routine wellness exams, preventive care, or urgent care, we offer comprehensive care for cats and dogs. We take pride in delivering high quality medical treatment in a comforting, family-oriented environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
