&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certified Veterinary Technician (CVT) – Join a Practice That Truly Values You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a passionate Certified Veterinary Technician looking for a place where your skills, voice, and well-being matter? We’re seeking a dedicated CVT to join our team and become part of a supportive, long-standing practice committed to exceptional care—for both our patients and our people.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You’ll Love Working With Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Loyal, Engaged Client Base: Our clients trust us and are deeply invested in their pets’ care, allowing you to fully utilize your technical skills and build meaningful relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stable, Experienced Team: Work alongside a fellow CVT who has been with us for over 20 years—just one example of the strong culture and longevity we’re proud of.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to High-Quality Medicine: We prioritize thorough, compassionate, and progressive veterinary care. Your expertise and input will always be valued.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible Scheduling: We understand that life outside of work matters. We’re happy to collaborate on a schedule that fits your needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;True Work-Life Balance: Burnout isn’t a badge of honor here. We actively support a healthy balance so you can thrive both professionally and personally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide skilled nursing care and patient monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in surgery and dentistry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform lab work and diagnostics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate and communicate effectively with clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with a team that respects and supports your role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current CVT license/credentials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A genuine passion for animal care and client education&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team-oriented mindset and positive attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re ready to join a practice where your experience is respected, your growth is encouraged, and your life outside of work is protected, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply today and discover a veterinary team that feels like home.&lt;/p&gt;
