&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot;&gt;Hours will be 34-40 per week.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;We are open Monday through Saturday.&amp;nbsp; Typical schedule for our technicians&amp;nbsp;are four 10-hour shifts&lt;/div&gt;
